definitions.definition: A metropolitan borough of Merseyside , England .
A village and civil parish (served by Sefton and Lunt Villages Parish Council) in Sefton borough , Merseyside , formerly in Lancashire ( OS grid ref SD3501 ) .
A suburb of Sydney , New South Wales .
A small town in Waimakariri district, Canterbury , New Zealand .
